abstract: International Weightlifting Federation bars Bulgaria from competing in 2016 Olympics after 11 lifters test positive for doping; other doping news noted.
lead_paragraph: Bulgaria will not compete in weight lifting at next year’s Rio de Janeiro Olympics after 11 lifters tested positive for doping this year.

headline.main: Bulgaria’s Weight Lifters Barred From Rio Olympics
